                   * 27: Destination out of order.
                   * 28: Invalid number format (incomplete number).
                   * 29: Facility rejected.
                   * 30: Response to STATUS ENQUIRY.
                   * 31: Normal, unspecified.

                 Resource unavailable:

                   * 34: No circuit/channel available.
